{
  "stem": "5248.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a extended family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we all lived together, or very close together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I spoke-- but older generation, like my grandparents-- I spoke Russian or sometimes Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then-- and then my-- my parents slowly were switching to Polish, which is not so different from Russian, except for the alphabet.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I spoke mostly Polish in school, because Polish was the language of instruction.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I start slowly speaking Polish with my parents as the years went by.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I also-- we had also many relatives from Germany, and they came to Poland once Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they lived with us for a while till they found a place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I-- so I learned from them a lot of German, because they spoke mostly German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never thought that I should take a-- a class or anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Although, school offers several languages that I had to take.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like Hebrew was taught in school as a foreign language.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--I heard about.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I personally did not feel it much, because we were trying-- I was very protected and sheltered.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And our school had very good reputation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, non-Jews were of course-- there was-- there was the population, Jewish people, which were majority, then Ukrainian people, and also Polish people, which were in administration in teaching.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before the war, I did not-- and I-- when I went still to-- to public school, I did not feel much of any anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to compete-- where there-- you had to-- my family wasn't Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was easier for me to compete with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My language was good-- and of course, amount of prestige my family had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there is so much said now on anti-Semitism in Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
